Chessboard

Class Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • Chessboard.Move

  • public class Move
extends java.lang.Object
    Class contains one chess move and it's score. Fields: - Integer: starting position - Integer: ending position - Piece: possibly captured piece during the move.
